<P>
QUAKE INSURANCE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
What's the difference between a property tax increase and mandatory homeowners' 
earthquake insurance (front page, Sept. 22)? Property taxes are deductible from 
income taxes and insurance premiums aren't. 
</P>
<P>
ELLEN STERN HARRIS 
</P>
<P>
Beverly Hills 
</P>
