Butterworth was also known for such children's books as "The Trouble With 
Jenny's Ear" and "The Narrow Passage." "The Enormous Egg" was produced on 
television by NBC Children's Theater. Butterworth also taught writing and 
literature at Hartford (Conn.) College for Women for 41 years. His other books 
include "A Visit to the Big House," "The First Blueberry Pig" and the 
