<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSWATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Marcida Dodson and Jeffrey A. Perlman 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAME GAME: The new name on the Big A outside Anaheim Stadium -- Great Western 
Bank -- will cost GW at least $125,000 a year. But that's nothing like the 
estimated $1 million a year GW pays to have Inglewood's sports arena called the 
Great Western Forum. . . . Could there be a "Great Western Anaheim Stadium" in 
