Photo, COLOR, Finally A Gay Traffic School meets on the patio of a popular Long 
Beach gay bar, with class conducted by A.J., right, a former California Highway 
Patrol officer. RANDY LEFFINGWELL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
